					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="15">1)</td>
						<td>Wash ark shells thoroughly and put in salt water to eliminate silts. Put in boiling water and if shells are open, drain and let cool. Leave one shell where ark shell is attached and take off the other shell. Place evenly on a plate with clam meat side upward.</td>
					</tr>
